## Contents

| File                     | Description |
|--------------------------|-------------|
| `Algorithms.java`        | Implements core algorithms: Bubble Sort, Insertion Sort, and Linear Search. |
| `Main.java`              | Entry point of the application. Accepts user input, runs selected algorithms, and records execution time. |
| `ChartGenerator.java` (optional) | (If added) Generates visual charts using JFreeChart based on algorithm timing. |
| `timing_data.csv`        | Stores recorded execution times for use in external charting tools (e.g., Excel). |
| `AlgorithmTimeChart.png` | Auto-generated visual chart comparing performance of algorithms by input size (if charting included). |

---

## Algorithms Implemented

### 1. Bubble Sort
- **Best Case**: O(n) – Already sorted
- **Worst Case**: O(n²) – Reverse sorted
- **Average Case**: O(n²)

### 2. Insertion Sort
- **Best Case**: O(n) – Already sorted
- **Worst Case**: O(n²) – Reverse sorted
- **Average Case**: O(n²)

### 3. Linear Search
- **Best Case**: O(1) – First element
- **Worst Case**: O(n) – Last element or not found
- **Average Case**: O(n/2)

---

